Enum Class Set

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Set>
pers.yuyanzhou.bubblebobble.support.Set
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Set>, Constable
public enum Set extends Enum<Set>
Set used to setting any GameObject property. Simply use this property by call Set.ENUM_PARAMETER.getInt() or Set.ENUM_PARAMETER.getDou()

YuyanZhou
